Yes I do - he - she - they used to take us to Seaport Sands. Seaport Sands was the place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3810732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5721260\charrsid12799702 How did you get there?
