Yes, I went to - school holidays, yes. I went to three school holidays. I went up with a Mr Helm - he used to be the schoolteacher, he come from a place called Dalton in Furness. That w
as where the iron mines were. And he took us - took us all down the iron mines once - one day. It was very good of him other times we used to go to Thurston Common.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3810732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5721260\charrsid12799702 Did you have any weeks holiday or anything like that?
