Mother, father and - and - well, our holidays then was a - pick for when we were on our school holidays. And - according to - see - me - me other brothers would be going away with the school for thei
r three weeks holiday. Then mother and father and - would likely be taken to the Isle of Man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3810732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5721260\charrsid12799702 How long for?
