ce - invoice lad - he used to be running from the offices to the cotton quay and the Sundry quay and bringing the invoices back to the office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3810732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5721260\charrsid12799702 What would the sundry quay be?
