Very well. Very well. And then I'd been doing that job for about three months and then he - they said - they'd put down as a - the - number taking. Number taking but that was a job - I had to be there at three forty-five of a morning to }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5209292\charrsid12799702 catch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5721260\charrsid12799702  the first goods coming in.
