ad, sundry quay, cotton quay. Used to shunt 'em down and - if I wasn't there when the goods came in well I'd be chasing all - all over the station trying to find out where they were - where they'd shunted. The - and the - the shunter'd say I've put two do
wn Chester Road - five on the sundry quay and all that sort of thing - where I'd go round and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5209292\charrsid12799702 tel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
