gether. Maybe the - the Rotunda together. I used to spend an evening in his house and he used to come - or he used to be - be in our house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3810732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5721260\charrsid12799702 Did your parents expect to know who you went with?
