 Yes. It was the type of man. Type of man came on - I know, I know. I used to be in Manchester - great big Victoria guards room there when I was guarding waiting for me - waiting for me next job. And used to hear the conversation - especially round about 
C
hristmas time. When Victoria and Exchange Station be busy. I've heard it said that - they've gone to Strangeways jail asking the - person in charge there if he had any chap - any prisoners coming out that had finished their time to send them over to him f
or a job. Now, when - when you consider it we had to have three references before we - well, that's what I say, it's the type of man who's come on the job. Us - us chaps in our younger days - we - we did.
